# Explanation

A simple application to play audio files. Inspired from the 
[PulseAudio Documentation](https://freedesktop.org/software/pulseaudio/doxygen/pacat-simple_8c-example.html)

The sound is played synchronously. 

This is just a practice program. The audio.c file will be used in another
project.

## Dependencies

`libpulse0 libpulse-dev [pulseaudio|pipewire-pulse]`

## Building

In the root directory, run `make`.
